  dialogueText: {fileID: 342461191}
  dialogueCanvas: {fileID: 759435600}
  lines:
  - "\"Yo! Glad you made it to the terrace. Tonight\u2019s the night.\""
  - Go ahead and grab that Diploma on the podium besides. It's your instrument for
    the show.
  - 'Controls: Left-Click for Confetti, G for Lightstick Glow, and F for the Sky
    Fireworks.'
  - Once you've got the hang of it, get ready. The show starts now!
  typeSpeed: 0.09
